Amir Khan wants to fight Kell Brook within the next 12 months . 
  Kell Brook has rejected the chance to fight Khan at Wembley in June . 
  Khan claims Brook is just looking for the 'one big payday' and is not even a big name in the UK . 
  Khan has denied that he will face Chris Algieri next month . 
  He says Brook is only interested in the fight because he needs the money . 
 